Titolo: Coloris

Anno: 1990

Descrizione: Coloris is a puzzle video game released in 1990 for the Amiga. It was originally published by Avesoft, a distributor of freeware and shareware disks.  Coloris is very similar to Sega's Columns, which itself is a variant of Tetris. 
A port to the Atari ST was only released as a preview; the full version was not published.